description: Retrieves the encryption configuration for resources and data in Amazon Web Services IoT FleetWise.

nested_items.name: kmsKeyId
nested_items.description: The ID of the KMS key that is used for encryption.

nested_items.name: encryptionType
nested_items.description: The type of encryption. Set to KMS_BASED_ENCRYPTION to use a KMS key that you own and manage. Set to FLEETWISE_DEFAULT_ENCRYPTION to use an Amazon Web Services managed key that is owned by the Amazon Web Services IoT FleetWise service account.

nested_items.name: errorMessage
nested_items.description: The error message that describes why encryption settings couldn't be configured, if applicable.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The time when encryption was configured in seconds since epoch (January 1, 1970 at midnight UTC time).

nested_items.name: lastModificationTime
nested_items.description: The time when encryption was last updated in seconds since epoch (January 1, 1970 at midnight UTC time).
